{"title":"小宋的校运会","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4598","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小辉辉的12个小宋想要举办一个SYXX校运会，他们的运动技能评分为1到1000000分。小辉辉想要给这12个小宋分成4组，每组3个小宋。为了比赛公平，他想要使得每个队伍的总技能分相对平均。小辉辉的算法是这样的，4组总技能分最大的S减去总技能分最小的s，使得这个差距最小。<br style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">由于小辉辉比较懒，所以请你帮助小辉辉找到一个分组方案，使得这个总技能分差距最小。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>12行，每行一个技能分。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出最小的S-s的值</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1</p><p>2</p><p>3</p><p>4</p><p>5</p><p>6</p><p>7</p><p>8</p><p>9</p><p>10</p><p>11</p><p>12</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>【样例解释】<br style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">分成4组(12,1,7), (9,8,3),(10,5,4), and (11,2,6)。最大20，最小19，差距为1</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}